title: Still have not gotten both icons from halloween
body: So i got the beat the teemoing icon(red teemo head) but never received the summoning little devil teemo one(little ghost with wispy things flying around it). Is this a bug or something because I had to have summoned him to beat him SOS help plz

replies.body:
Hmm, can you reach out in a [**support ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so one of our specialists can take a look at see what we can do?
